# TeachersPet

TeachersPet is a computer-vision–based monitoring tool that detects background people and triggers visual/audio effects when a teacher is detected.
This alerts the currently used app if the user is doing irrelevant tasks.

---

## Requirements

- macOS / Windows
- Python 3.10 or newer
- Built in camera

---

## (macOS only) Install Homebrew

If you don’t have Homebrew installed:

/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"

---

## (macOS only) Install opencv

brew install opencv
brew instal ffmpeg

---

## for installing python packages

pip install .
